OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with further showers,
OL,7,Fthese focused across the north. Clear
OL,8,Fspells developing overnight,
OL,9,Fparticularly across southern areas
OL,10,Fwhere showers largely die out.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FMany enjoying a dry day with
OL,13,Flight winds and good sunny spells
OL,14,Fdeveloping into the afternoon.
OL,15,FHowever, some early light showers will
OL,16,Fappear, chiefly confined to the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
