OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMost
OL,6,Fdry during Monday, with sunshine
OL,7,Fturning hazy for the afternoon.
OL,8,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,9,Fcrossing the area from the southwest
OL,10,Ffrom late Monday and through Tuesday
OL,11,Fand Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
